{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s001", "order": 1, "text": "**Objective**", "char_start": 0, "char_end": 13, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 3}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s002", "order": 2, "text": "Implement an automated incident classification system that categorizes events as Low, Medium, or High severity within 30 seconds of log ingestion.", "char_start": 16, "char_end": 162, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 24}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s003", "order": 3, "text": "This rapid triaging will streamline incident response and reduce noise for security teams.", "char_start": 163, "char_end": 253, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 14}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s004", "order": 4, "text": "**Classification Engine**", "char_start": 255, "char_end": 280, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 4}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s005", "order": 5, "text": "The AI-powered engine ingests three primary inputs: log severity (e.g., error level, frequency), source IP reputation (internal threat intel scores), and an anomaly score derived from behavior baselines.", "char_start": 283, "char_end": 486, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 40}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s006", "order": 6, "text": "Severity thresholds are dynamically tuned using a feedback loop informed by incident resolution data and false-positive rates, ensuring adaptive precision over time.", "char_start": 487, "char_end": 652, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 26}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s007", "order": 7, "text": "**Alert Routing**", "char_start": 654, "char_end": 671, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 4}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s008", "order": 8, "text": "Classified alerts are routed based on severity:  \n- **Low** ➜ Added to the Jira security backlog for periodic review.", "char_start": 674, "char_end": 791, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 23}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s009", "order": 9, "text": "- **Medium** ➜ Posted in Slack `#sec-ops` for real-time triage by analysts.", "char_start": 794, "char_end": 869, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 22}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s010", "order": 10, "text": "- **High** ➜ Triggered as a PagerDuty \"P1\" alert, with immediate escalation.", "char_start": 872, "char_end": 948, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 19}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s011", "order": 11, "text": "**SLA & Metrics**  \nSystem must maintain ≥ 95% classification accuracy.", "char_start": 950, "char_end": 1021, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 14}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s012", "order": 12, "text": "Alerts should be delivered within 60 seconds for 95% of cases (P95 latency).", "char_start": 1022, "char_end": 1098, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 17}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s013", "order": 13, "text": "**Audit & Reporting**", "char_start": 1100, "char_end": 1121, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 5}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s014", "order": 14, "text": "Each classification is logged in the `incident_audit` table with original log content, predicted severity, and the model version used.", "char_start": 1124, "char_end": 1258, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 23}
{"doc_id": "1c41bae5-3fb5-59b3-b411-42f628ba6828", "req_id": "REQ-130", "sent_id": "REQ-130::s015", "order": 15, "text": "Records are retained for a minimum of one year to support compliance and post-incident reviews.", "char_start": 1259, "char_end": 1354, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 18}
